{"tid":2009506,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港鐵乘客行李重量收緊至23公斤","createTime":"2020-05-09T18:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T23:21:20.000Z","uid":5195,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"26c1982bbe81dc52513558a612d91f75390ce20b","tid":2009506,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2013-MTR.WEIGHT.1000.0402.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2013-MTR.WEIGHT.1000.0402.jpg&h=6a748d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵乘客行李重量收緊至23公斤<br />\n星島日報<br />\n2013年2月1日 16:55<br />\n因應香港特區政府的要求，港鐵公司會由下星期一起，將東鐵綫乘客行李重量限制由目前最高32 公斤收緊至最高23 公斤。同時，繼上水站、粉嶺站、羅湖站及落馬洲站的指定出入口設置地磅，要求乘客將較重行李過磅檢查後，東鐵綫會在另外兩個車站包括大埔墟站和火炭站實施同類安排。<br />\n<br />\n新設定的23 公斤行李重量上限是參考旅遊業界現有的標準，試驗為期三個月。若乘客携帶的行李超過重量上限或尺寸(長、闊及高總和不超過170 厘米)的規定，將不獲准使用鐵路服務。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵會加派人手和加強車站及車廂的巡查。目前東鐵綫共有39 名港鐵附例特檢隊隊員，負責在東鐵綫沿綫車站執行港鐵附例，他們並由一隊超過90 名的合約保安員所支援。附例特檢隊會增加20 名人手，至59 名隊員，今次已是「特檢隊」在四個月內第二度增加人手。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵會繼續與警方緊密合作，監察東鐵綫的情況，確保為乘客提供舒適的乘車環境。"},{"pid":"1e7e2ef0edf68627ecfc9ce8487633d46976db3f","tid":2009506,"uid":1327,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:58:28.000Z","msg":"岩岩好夠d 伙記運冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219207514588dd2e8e3dc9200c75e1def990dde9","tid":2009506,"uid":114891,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:59:33.000Z","msg":"<del>運兵列車</del><br />\n運冰列車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7665603d3f67fcbaff82793116ace94c80e18147","tid":2009506,"uid":33028,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e7e2ef0edf68627ecfc9ce8487633d46976db3f","tid":2009506,"uid":1327,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:58:28.000Z","msg":"岩岩好夠d 伙記運冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T19:05:46.000Z","msg":"2003<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27855e9c2d5c55ac23a986075316c29165ba686","tid":2009506,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T19:06:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩好夠d 伙記運冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>2013<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7c6a535cf89d14c0d4d93b5f243eed0c78d442bd","tid":2009506,"uid":232185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T19:15:39.000Z","msg":"其實根本唔check<br />\n講笑都無意義"},{"pid":"ba17447298379be50b38f52f6524aca78230bf2f","tid":2009506,"uid":37058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T19:37:48.000Z","msg":"原來方便3萬隻運野"},{"pid":"569eda5d4236dce113e2afeffa7416139b74b8e0","tid":2009506,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T20:19:14.000Z","msg":"攪到批25kg 貨要分兩次運，快啲譴責港鐵"},{"pid":"acd64af58aab5403913bb1fccb44908c4dc17fe3","tid":2009506,"uid":164965,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T23:21:20.000Z","msg":"old news<br />\n拉"}]}